ygData.messageBody:
Hi,

Please excuse my off topic post but i'd like to have your opinion on the
following. I've started playing
on my Compaq Pressario 1692 and I find that the display is very dark.
Also, a bug exists that I can see
the top of trees and Undead creatures through Montains, dunes, etc.
It's fun to be able to do that but
rather anoying when i'm in big forests as I see ALL the trees and skele
around.

I'm supposedly using a Rage Lt Pro AGP 2X, version 5.35-c57X on this
laptop, anyone know if they mixed up
the Drivers or if any update exists ? Any info is grealy appreciated

Thanks.

Fause Note
Level 25 Bard (Bristlebane)
Spz@...
